<h1>Optiv Promotional Merchandise Use Policy</h1>

<p>The goal of this policy document is to provide Optiv employees with guidance on obtaining and using Optiv promotional merchandise. The use of Optiv premium items reinforces our company identity, brand and culture. By creating a uniform approach, we can help ensure the representation of our brand and corporate mark remains intact, while promoting Optiv through the use of promotional materials.</p>

<table>
