		<tr>
			<td width="20%">Definition</td>
			<td width="80%">Optiv promotional merchandise (AKA swag or premium items) include, but are not limited to, apparel,  office supplies, bags, drinkware, sporting goods, gifts and other items bearing the Optiv logo.</td>
		</tr>

		<tr>
			<td>Optiv Brand</td>
			<td>Optiv places a high priority on the representation of the Optiv corporate mark and produces promotional items of high quality, which reinforce the Optiv brand. Optiv promotional items should not be produced on an individual employee basis. Should a unique situation or request arise, please contact <a href="mailto:creative@optiv.com">creative@optiv.com</a> to review and approve any logo placement and item selection for promotional materials.</td>
		</tr>

		<tr>
			<td>Optiv Store</td>
			<td>Optiv has established an online company store to be the primary location for employees wishing to obtain Optiv promotional merchandise.  Featured items have been pre-selected based on quality and adherence to meeting standards set with the Optiv brand. Access to the Optiv store can be found on the Optiv SSO (Single Sign-On) dashboard. The website is intended for employee use only and should not be shared with third parties, clients or partners for use directly or indirectly.</td>
		</tr>

